name: PepeTarot Cards
description: fOracle is an RNG based divination protocol built on Fantom Opera. Using fOracle, diviners may seek their fortune by drawing a PepeTarot card and receive that card as an NFT. PepeTarot is a digital tarot card deck based on the original Rider-Waite Tarot deck art and symbolism. The first fOracle drop-PepeTarot Edition 0- launched on July 13th, 2021 with a total of 111 PepeTarot Cards minted.
